{"type": "article", "id": 28064, "title": "Burberry COO 离职，以及， Sacai 苹果表带很不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-06-12T11:50:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2871, "name": "Apple Watch"}, {"id": 7532, "name": "表带"}, {"id": 1190, "name": "伦敦男装周"}, {"id": 14026, "name": "度假系列"}, {"id": 190, "name": "时装秀"}, {"id": 16820, "name": "艺术总监"}, {"id": 3786, "name": "包袋"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}, {"id": 7612, "name": "Disney"}, {"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}, {"id": 7469, "name": "Lemaire"}, {"id": 3322, "name": "Givenchy"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 1453, "name": "MCM"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 905, "name": "Dover Street Market"}, {"id": 12231, "name": "Sacai"}, {"id": 19143, "name": "Public School"}, {"id": 231, "name": "Apple"}, {"id": 16447, "name": "Christopher Raeburn"}, {"id": 7576, "name": "Christophe Lemaire"}, {"id": 28456, "name": "Bella Hadid"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133859YbGTW5LuDKO83qJv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/human-resources/david-dombrow-rejoined-under-armour-chief-creative-officer-10449004/\">Under Armour 聘请首席创意官</a></b>｜上周，运动品牌 Under Armour 宣布由 Dave Dombrow 担任首席创意官。后者曾任 UA 高级副总裁、执掌鞋履及配饰的创意部门，今年 2 月离职后一度有传闻称他将加入 Nike，但因非竞争条款限制，至少在 2017 年才有可能在 Nike 任职。UA 提供了更高的新职位吸引其回归。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Burberry-COO-John-Smith-to-leave-company-in-2017,702372.html\"><b>Burberry 首席营运官离职</b></a>｜Burberry 近日宣布首席营运官（COO） John Smith 离职， John Smith 从 2013 年 3 月起担任 Burberry 的 COO 职位，2004 年至 2012 年任英国广播公司商业分支 CEO 职位。Burberry 现任 CEO Christopher Bailey 将为公司寻找合适人选接替 Smith，这是他首次决定高级管理人员的任职，他表示将寻求兼具营运经验的零售专家。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/markets-news/ready-to-wear-sportswear/vince-holding-reported-q1-loss-apparel-fashion-contemporary-10445813/\"><b>Vince 一季度净亏损</b></a>｜Vince 集团近日发布财报，截至 4 月 30 日的一季度， 净亏损达到 190 万美元，而去年同期净收入为 250 万美元。净销售额从 5980 万美元上涨了 13.1% 至 6760 万美元。对于总利润的降低，公司表示主要原因为产品改革及继续战略投资。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/mens-health-editor-in-chief-bill-phillips-out-michael-lafavore-letter-maria-rodale-10451037/\"><b><i>Men’s Health</i> 主编离职</b></a>｜<i>Men’s Health </i>杂志主编 Bill Phillips 将离职，这是自从集团董事长及 CEO Maria Rodale 去年任命 Michael Lafavore 为编辑主任后引发的一系列离职中最新的一环，此前离职人士包括高级编辑 Matt Marion、副总裁兼编辑 Peter Moore、高级艺术总监 Mike Schnaidt 等等。Phillips 于 2012 年 11 月成为副总裁及主编，在 Rodale 集团工作了 13 年。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2016/06/coach-mickey-mouse-disney-collab\"><b>Bella Hadid 又为 Givenchy 拍大片</b></a>｜超模 Bella Hadid 风头不减，继拿下 Dior 美妆产品代言，为 Givenchy 拍摄秋季大片后，又为 Givenchy 旗下新牛仔产品线拍摄广告。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133838UpAWoHtEmiLPr8VR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0730897\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2><b>一些值得一看的：</b></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/resort-2017/new-york/public-school/review/\">Public School 2017 度假系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133839ivqVl1E9WjNcTRre.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133839E3oN1DPncIrzySxw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133840mtjAhox93CZNvqu4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133840eEXKkN9F1UOihyvq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133841B7q1RT6Z3n8L0FOj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133841bi3crFAaQZLGE2CS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133842HkIrnd35Bb1SA7TP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>Coach 庆祝 75 周年，推出<a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2016/06/coach-mickey-mouse-disney-collab\">限量迪士尼合作系列</a>，</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133842oi31ehrvPQU2kg7q.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133843oVDXlR6fO3PABxqj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133843Jlr6IaGCB8yhHgE2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133844grKT137w0bG8HJkq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021338447kPdM4oylp5uHC19.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">伦敦男装周第二天，为庆祝品牌成立 40 周年，<a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/mens-spring-collections-2017/london/mcm-x-christopher-raeburn/review/\">德国皮具品牌 MCM 与英国设计师 Christopher Raeburn 合作</a>，推出了一场时装秀：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133845dPhxa35T7V2sc4Hw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133845KpzDsNQugv8C3rZB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133846WlXfnAiHVRrJMY0e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133847HWRLubs5wCADPVJT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021338487VkIw6NyWdBJSsPU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021338490XBihW7z5J9feLR2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>Gucci 进驻东京、纽约、伦敦和北京的 Dover Street Market 后，<a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/gucci-dover-street-market-collaboration/\">近日推出 Dover Street Market 限定系列商品</a>，将在以上几座城市的 DSM 内发售。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133850RdSEzmYqN2J01I5U.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021338500EJ2eTd3rOBMZpuH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133851FXBEi46M9GNaVg3A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133851EdpqDOVeBYg8IsTk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133852K3obEXp4gR7fPwV8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133852ohAltQ6VYEJ319RT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/craig-green-2017-spring-summer-collection-is-a-study-in-form-and-movement\">Craig Green 2017 春夏系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133853atPl2cB6JDxpMREX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7595682\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133853TMBwYcVuI8CbfSFp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7595682\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133853hAHM3eTClRzVano5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7595682\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133854uDyT7zN290l8xhfb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7595682\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>日本设计师阿部千登势(Chitose Abe)创立的 Sacai 品牌，<a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/sacai-collaborates-apple-watch-strap-10451095/\">为苹果设计了一款 Apple Watch 表带</a>，鳄鱼皮和金属链条的混搭：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021338553Yf19GQ5TlqAIFWe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"> Moschino 在洛杉矶发布 <a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2016/06/tommy-hilfiger-memoir\">2017 早春度假及春季女装系列大秀</a>，现场与 Livit 公司合作，使用 VR 技术进行流媒体直播：                       </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133855cMOB698YplKimJZt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133856VFbICjKBMqDWoQlt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133856glFQ2P0bzmrLxs6a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133857P2xV1seUZ4SuJvgd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133857LtVcfYMyUrjdogJK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021338580eTqE9LkK2Fasg81.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133858T4wn0asHWrdSIjOy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}